data.description:
Nestled in the vibrant heart of Indialantic lies this exceptional residence, a quintessential emblem of coveted beachside living. With an unparalleled location mere moments from the sun-kissed shores, lush parks, bustling shopping districts, and an array of exquisite dining establishments, this home encapsulates the essence of coastal charm. Radiating a timeless allure, this gem beckons with its adorned front and back covered porches, inviting you to savor the coastal breeze and embrace laid-back moments. The low-maintenance backyard, adorned with astroturf, creates a serene oasis perfect for leisurely lounging by the inviting pool—a sanctuary amidst the bustle of daily life.
Positioned on a generous corner lot, this residence stands out with ample parking options, catering effortlessly to multiple vehicles, boats, or an RV, fulfilling the desires of avid adventurers or hobby enthusiasts.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Evident at first glance is the pride of ownership, meticulously reflected in the pristine interior and meticulously curated exterior spaces. Recent enhancements, including a fresh interior paint job and new carpeting in all bedrooms, further elevate the allure and comfort of this abode.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'This captivating home is a testament to coastal elegance, an idyllic haven awaiting those who seek a seamless blend of comfort, convenience, and the allure of beachside living. Don't miss the chance to claim this slice of paradiseschedule your appointment today and secure your place amidst the coastal splendor before it slips away.'||chr(10)||'
